productParameters.detailedDescription:
The ANZ Plus Standard Variable Rate Loan is a variable rate loan that is full of features and it gives you the flexibility to react to the changes in your life or circumstances.

Benefits such as:
• the ability to make extra repayments, and
• no early repayment costs if you decide to sell your property

A variable rate loan means that the interest rate that is applied to your home loan can change. This means your minimum repayments decrease when interest rates go down, and your minimum repayments will increase when interest rates go up
